The syntax of our wiki pages is based on the [markdown syntax](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown#Syntax_examples). 

The restrictions are:

* no html/xml tags allowed

The additions are:

* \[\[Topic\]\] - to add a link to a page in this same wiki
* \[\[\[Topic\]\]\] - to add a link to a page in wikipedia
* \{\{special code\}\} - special code

